trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `Command` event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control button in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> object is clicked.
trans-unit.target: `Command` 이벤트가 때는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>의 컨트롤 단추는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField>개체를 클릭 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs class is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods to access information about the event that was raised.
trans-unit.target: DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs 클래스에서 내부적으로 사용 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드 발생 한 이벤트에 대 한 정보에 액세스할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of the DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs class, see the DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs constructor.
trans-unit.target: DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs 클래스의 인스턴스에 대 한 초기 속성 값 목록은 DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs 생성자를 참조 하십시오.
